掌控cesium的控件


baseLayerPicker///控制的是底图控件
下面代码是控制底图按钮的img的logo
viewer.baseLayerPicker.container.getElementsByClassName("cesium-baseLayerPicker-selected")[0].setAttribute('style', 'display:block;');

viewer.baseLayerPicker.container.getElementsByClassName("cesium-baseLayerPicker-selected")[0].setAttribute('src', '/lib/cesium/Build/Cesium/Widgets/Images/ImageryProviders/esriWorldImagery.png');